title: How to Watch Election Night Like a Pro
description: Strategists are watching a few East Coast races that could be called early, offering a rough road map to the entire country.
dc:creator: Blake Hounshell

media:content.media:credit: Kristen Zeis for The New York Times
media:content.media:description: If Representative Elaine Luria survives her race in Virginia, it will most likely be a good night for Democrats.
